{"tid":683510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬sell新波衫冇賤種朗有巴利","createTime":"2018-05-29T18:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T03:47:22.000Z","uid":20634,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"56c8a94b74c1f97bf4e32fbcc0892a4edf6b17a4","tid":683510,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/1/261/21609020261/21611531269_600x389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F261%2F21609020261%2F21611531269_600x389.jpg&h=a425f328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真？皇家馬德里官方公佈新球衣，但主角居然少了基斯坦奴朗拿度，這是離隊先兆嗎？<br />\n<br />\n歐聯3連霸大軍皇家馬德里今日公佈2018/19球季新主場和作客戰衣，加里夫巴利（Gareth Bale）、賓施馬、馬些路和拿祖費南迪斯等型格登場。但是，球迷找了很久，居然找不到大紅人基斯坦如朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）的身影，與離隊的傳言不謀而合，令人無限聯想。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，這位葡萄牙巨星在歐聯決賽後暗示離隊，此言令隊長沙治奧拉莫斯甚為不滿。無論如何，其去向表明可以在短時間內揭開謎底。<br />\n<br />\n說回新球衣，主場波衫變化不大，贊助商名字改為adidas，肩上的間條顏色由黑變藍。客場波衫方面，藍色被飛走，基本上被黑色包圍。新球衣已公開發售，成人版售價為69.95鎊。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 球會官網圖片"},{"pid":"3c5b4ce2db181463130070d6e09e3af43b9fbcbe","tid":683510,"uid":283,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"c朗好似nike<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa09f437f9a9323af8e6f30551333062f641c77f","tid":683510,"uid":6676,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.fifa.com/mm/photo/world-match-centre/clubfootball/02/44/33/30/2443330_big-lnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.fifa.com%2Fmm%2Fphoto%2Fworld-match-centre%2Fclubfootball%2F02%2F44%2F33%2F30%2F2443330_big-lnd.jpg&h=8adc12b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一撚樣咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d80d00a794908997047edc49b5d3146ee25847","tid":683510,"uid":20634,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:38:50.000Z","msg":"<i